text: bike committee update: got an email from Beam with a few follow-ups to our list of demands / polite requests
- badged cage enclosure around the current basement parking : Received pricing.  Hope to do this in the future, but do not have budget available at this time.
- retrofit racks with cables to accommodate standard u-lock throw  :  Cables are on order, should be installed late November or early December.
-  active ventilation in the 3rd floor bathrooms : Out to bid with two contractors.  We hope to move on this upon receipt of pricing.
- if not a cage, use tamper-proof bolts on the rack mount :  On order, will install when we install the cables.
security cameras / lockers / stairway retrofit are things they will continue to consider but will likely not get to in the near future
There's some good stuff in there. Thanks for representing us <@U0260V1BX> !
np - i'm glad they were so receptive
